                    h3 Jane
                    em Partner | Lead Stylist
                    div(id="janebio",style="display:none;color:white")
                        strong Jane is co-owner of the salon and leads and mentors our Artistic Team here at OPC. She is also our resident color expert. Jane crafted her early career in Florida, where she became a Redken Master Stylist and color maven. Ten years later, she was ready for New York…and New York was ready for Jane. Jane lives in Greenpoint and is excited to bring her talents to Ft. Greene. “The neighborhood needs easy access to stellar hair services! I love the energy, diversity, and artistic expression found in the most unlikely of places in this city.” Jane’s approach is all about precision – delivered with warmth, sincerity and fun. Her instinctive reading of her clients needs, coupled with exemplary service standards has given our team pride and inspiration.
            .col-xs-6.col-md-4#jessica(style="padding:20px")
                center
