                    div(id="jennibio",style="display:none;color:white")
                        strong Jenni is a New York native with 8 years experience as a stylist and make up artist. She is a Certified Colorist for Redken, where she trained extensively at the Redken Exchange on Fifth Avenue. In conjunction with her salon work, Jenni has traveled the country training upcoming stylists on color theory and application. Wanting to expand her knowledge as an artist, Jenni earned her BFA in photography at the Fashion Institute of Technology. “Studying both art forms truly allowed me to look at the hair and individual with a unique perspective. As stylists, we create wearable art on every client in our chair!”
                        
            .col-xs-6#cori(style="padding:20px")
