                        strong Cori Norton, our brand new super-stylist is another Floridian transplant happily received into Brooklyn! Cori’s love and passion for hair began nearly a decade ago in 2005, where she attended Redken’s Salon Professional Academy in Tampa, Florida. Over the years she has trained with some of the leading hair artists in the industry, and focussed on education through classes at Redken’s 5th Ave. headquarters. She has worked on commercial and photo shoots, including styling hair for the Tampa Bay Buccaneer Cheerleaders. Cori enjoys every aspect of doing hair but particularly loves to focus on curly hair, blondes and color corrections. Cori is a warm, friendly and talented addition to the team.
